Author: Matryx.ai
Title: [ANN] [MTX] | Matryx Token Sale Announcement
Body: Thank you for your support, we are confident in our already existent products and encourage you to check them out.  We believe that with the community's help, we can build another great service; blockchain, VR, and research are a trio that could be incredibly potent. The 3 rounds are just an example of how the platform works. Verified Solutions will be determined by the person or institution posting the bounty.  Feel free to ask this account any questions you may have regarding Matryx.

Author: Matryx.ai
Title: [ANN] [MTX] | Matryx Token Sale Announcement
Body: MATRYX REWARDS PROGRAM matryx.ai/rewards  Matryx aims to solve a huge problem — to democratize scientific research and remove redundancies and barriers to entry in all fields of innovation. That’s why we need a large community of innovators and contributors who believe in the power of global, decentralized collaboration. To help build this, we are excited to announce the launch of the Matryx Rewards Program — a fun way to help engage the community and earn MTX while you’re at it!  We’ve set aside 150,000 MTX to help support community growth during our token sale! From today until October 13th, or the end of the token sale, you can earn MTX by engaging with our community and creating content on Youtube, Twitter, Blogs, and Forums. Of the tokens issued, 20,000 are set aside for special projects that our community comes up with.  If you have ideas, you can reach us at rewards@matryx.ai.  To see the ways that you can earn, head over to matryx.ai/rewards to see what you can earn, and register to participate!   MATRYX REWARDS PROGRAM matryx.ai/rewards
